    <a href="/msa.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">MSA</a> and
    <a href="/dpa.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">DPA</a> are standardized. Email <a href="mailto:procurement@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">procurement@replicate.info</a> if you need pre-signed versions.
  </p>

  <p class="font-medium mb-1">Sales tax</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Sales tax (e.g., VAT, GST, or US state) is calculated automatically at checkout (if applicable). If your organization is tax-exempt (e.g., nonprofit, public sector, international reverse charge), email <a href="mailto:procurement@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">procurement@replicate.info</a> with your exemption certificate and we'll apply it before issuing the invoice.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-medium">Refund Policy</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    We do not offer refunds once an invoice is paid, even if usage stops. We help fix erroneous payments.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-medium">Support</p>
